gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Trail Blazers 99, Raptors 91
gameRecap.excerpt: The Trail Blazers defeated the Raptors, 99-91. Jerami Grant recorded 22 points and six rebounds for the Trail Blazers, with Malcolm Brogdon adding 21 points, five assists, and three rebounds in the victory. Scottie Barnes tallied 20 points, 12 rebounds, and two assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Trail Blazers improve to 1-3 on the season, while the Raptors fall to 1-3.
